msgid "# GLM-5.2"
msgstr "# GLM-5.2"

msgid "## Introduction"
msgstr "## 简介"

msgid ""
"[GLM-5.2](https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-5.2) uses a Mixture-of-Experts "
"(MoE) architecture and targets complex systems engineering and long-horizon "
"agentic tasks."
msgstr ""
"[GLM-5.2](https://huggingface.co/zai-org/GLM-5.2) "
"采用混合专家（MoE）架构，面向复杂系统工程和长周期智能体任务。"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of the model, including "
"supported features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-"
"node and multi-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr "本文档将展示该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点与多节点部署、精度及性能评估。"

msgid "## Supported Features"
msgstr "## 支持特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型的支持特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置方法。"

msgid "## Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 环境准备"

msgid "### Model Weight"
msgstr "### 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `GLM-5.2`(BF16 version): requires 2 Atlas 800 A3 (128G × 8) node or 4 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) node.[Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-5.2).\n"
"- `GLM-5.2-w8a8`: requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (128G × 8) node or 2 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 8) node.[Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/GLM-5.2-w8a8).\n"
"- You can use [msmodelslim](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/msmodelslim) to quantize the model directly."
msgstr ""
"- `GLM-5.2`（BF16版本）：需要2个Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）节点或4个Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/ZhipuAI/GLM-5.2)。\n"
"- `GLM-5.2-w8a8`：需要1个Atlas 800 A3（128G × 8）节点或2个Atlas 800 A2（64G × 8）节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/GLM-5.2-w8a8)。\n"
"- 您可以使用[msmodelslim](https://gitcode.com/Ascend/msmodelslim)直接对模型进行量化。"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to the shared directory of "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`"
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享目录中，例如 `/root/.cache/`"

msgid "### Installation"
msgstr "### 安装"

msgid "You can use our official docker image to run GLM-5.2 directly."
msgstr "您可以直接使用官方Docker镜像运行GLM-5.2。"

msgid "Start the docker image on your each node."
msgstr "在每个节点上启动Docker镜像。"

msgid "Start the docker image on each of your nodes."
msgstr "在每个节点上启动Docker镜像。"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to set up environment"
" on each node."
msgstr "如需部署多节点环境，需要在每个节点上进行环境配置。"

msgid "## Deployment"
msgstr "## 部署"

msgid "### Single-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 单节点部署"

msgid ""
"- Quantized model `glm-5.2-w8a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × "
"16) ."
msgstr "- 量化模型 `glm-5.2-w8a8` 可部署在1个Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）上。"

msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

msgid ""
"**Notice:**\n"
"The parameters are explained as follows:"
msgstr ""
"**注意：**\n"
"参数说明如下："

msgid ""
"- For single-node deployment, we recommend using `dp1tp16` and turn off "
"expert parallel in low-latency scenarios."
msgstr "- 对于单节点部署，在低延迟场景下建议使用 `dp1tp16` 并关闭专家并行。"

msgid "### Multi-node Deployment"
msgstr "### 多节点部署"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to verify multi-node "
"communication according to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication)."
msgstr ""
"如需部署多节点环境，需按照[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-"
"communication)验证多节点通信。"

msgid "=== \"A3 series\""
msgstr "=== \"A3系列\""

msgid "- `glm-5.2-w8a8`: can be deployed on 2 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16)."
msgstr "- `glm-5.2-w8a8`：可部署在2个Atlas 800 A3（64G × 16）上。"

msgid "Run the following scripts on two nodes respectively."
msgstr "分别在两个节点上运行以下脚本。"

msgid "=== \"A2 series\""
msgstr "=== \"A2系列\""

msgid "- `glm-5.2-w8a8`: can be deployed on 2 Atlas 800 A2 (64G × 32)."
msgstr "- `glm-5.2-w8a8`：可部署在2个Atlas 800 A2（64G × 32）上。"

msgid "**node 0**"
msgstr "**节点0**"

msgid "**node 1**"
msgstr "**节点1**"

msgid "### Co-located Deployment on 4 Nodes (200k context)"
msgstr "### 4节点共置部署（200k上下文）"

msgid ""
"In a co-located (mixed) deployment, prefill and decode run together on the "
"same nodes, in contrast to the disaggregated setup below. The following "
"templates deploy `GLM-5.2` across 4 nodes with `DP4 TP8` (`data-parallel-"
"size-local=1` per node), a 200k context window, and MTP "
"(`num_speculative_tokens=5`). Node 0 hosts the API server and is the DP "
"master; Node 1 to Node 3 run with `--headless`. Prefix caching is disabled "
"(`--no-enable-prefix-caching`) in this configuration. All IPs, NIC names, "
"ports and weight paths are placeholders."
msgstr ""
"在共置（混合）部署中，prefill和decode在同一节点上共同运行，与下文分离式部署不同。以下模板在4个节点上以`DP4 "
"TP8`（每节点`data-parallel-size-"
"local=1`）、200k上下文窗口和MTP（`num_speculative_tokens=5`）部署`GLM-5.2`。节点0承载API服务器并作为DP主节点；节点1至节点3以`--headless`运行。此配置中禁用前缀缓存（`--no-"
"enable-prefix-caching`）。所有IP、网卡名称、端口和权重路径均为占位符。"

msgid "**Node 0** (API server / DP master):"
msgstr "**节点0**（API服务器/DP主节点）："

msgid "**Node 1** (headless, `--data-parallel-start-rank 1`):"
msgstr "**节点1**（无头模式，`--data-parallel-start-rank 1`）："

msgid ""
"Node 2 and Node 3 use the same script as Node 1, with `--data-parallel-"
"start-rank` set to `2` and `3` respectively (and `node0_ip` pointing to Node"
" 0)."
msgstr ""
"节点2和节点3使用与节点1相同的脚本，分别设置`--data-parallel-start-"
"rank`为`2`和`3`（并将`node0_ip`指向节点0）。"

msgid "### Prefill-Decode Disaggregation"
msgstr "### Prefill-Decode分离式部署"

msgid ""
"We'd like to show the deployment guide of `GLM-5` on multi-node environment "
"with 1P1D for better performance."
msgstr "我们将展示`GLM-5`在多节点环境下采用1P1D配置以获得更优性能的部署指南。"

msgid ""
"Prefill-Decode disaggregation can be deployed on 4 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 32)."
msgstr "Prefill-Decode分离式部署可部署在4个Atlas 800 A3（64G × 32）上。"

msgid "Before you start, please"
msgstr "开始之前，请"

msgid "1. prepare the script `launch_online_dp.py` on each node:"
msgstr "1. 在每个节点上准备脚本 `launch_online_dp.py`："

msgid "2. prepare the script `run_dp_template.sh` on each node."
msgstr "2. 在每个节点上准备脚本 `run_dp_template.sh`。"

msgid ""
"To support a 200k context window on the stage of prefill, the parameter `\"layer_sharding\": [\"q_b_proj\"]` needs to be added to `--additional_config` on each prefill node.\n"
"    1. Prefill node 0"
msgstr ""
"为在prefill阶段支持200k上下文窗口，需要在每个prefill节点的`--additional_config`中添加参数`\"layer_sharding\": [\"q_b_proj\"]`。\n"
"    1. Prefill节点0"

msgid ""
"Once the preparation is done, you can start the server with the following "
"command on each node:"
msgstr "准备工作完成后，可在每个节点上使用以下命令启动服务器："

msgid "1. Prefill node 0"
msgstr "1. Prefill节点0"

msgid "2. Prefill node 1"
msgstr "2. Prefill节点1"

msgid "3. Decode node 0"
msgstr "3. Decode节点0"

msgid "4. Decode node 1"
msgstr "4. Decode节点1"

msgid "#### Deployment on 8 Atlas 800 A2"
msgstr "#### 在8个Atlas 800 A2上部署"

msgid ""
"On Atlas 800 A2, where each node exposes 8 cards, the same global P/D "
"topology (Prefill `DP4 TP8`, Decode `DP8 TP4`) is split across 8 nodes: 4 "
"prefill nodes hosting 1 DP rank each (8 cards per rank), and 4 decode nodes "
"hosting 2 DP ranks each (4 cards per rank). The `launch_online_dp.py` above "
"is reused as-is. The prefill side enables FlashComm1 and DSA CP; the decode "
"side enables MLAPO and `DYNAMIC_EPLB` with a `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` graph. Both "
"sides enable prefix caching and MTP (`num_speculative_tokens=3`). All IPs, "
"NIC names, ports and weight paths below are placeholders."
msgstr ""
"在Atlas 800 A2上，每个节点暴露8张卡，相同的全局P/D拓扑（Prefill `DP4 TP8`，Decode `DP8 "
"TP4`）分布在8个节点上：4个prefill节点各承载1个DP rank（每rank 8卡），4个decode节点各承载2个DP rank（每rank"
" 4卡）。上述`launch_online_dp.py`保持不变直接复用。Prefill端启用FlashComm1和DSA "
"CP；Decode端启用MLAPO和带`FULL_DECODE_ONLY`图的`DYNAMIC_EPLB`。两端均启用前缀缓存和MTP（`num_speculative_tokens=3`）。以下所有IP、网卡名称、端口和权重路径均为占位符。"

msgid "`run_dp_template.sh` for the prefill nodes:"
msgstr "prefill节点的`run_dp_template.sh`："

msgid "`run_dp_template.sh` for the decode nodes:"
msgstr "`run_dp_template.sh` 用于解码节点："

msgid ""
"Once the preparation is done, start the server with the following commands:"
msgstr "准备工作完成后，使用以下命令启动服务器："

msgid ""
"1. Prefill nodes — run on `$node_p0_ip`, `$node_p1_ip`, `$node_p2_ip`, "
"`$node_p3_ip` with `--dp-rank-start` `0/1/2/3`:"
msgstr ""
"1. 预填充节点 — 在 `$node_p0_ip`、`$node_p1_ip`、`$node_p2_ip`、`$node_p3_ip` 上运行，使用 "
"`--dp-rank-start` `0/1/2/3`："

msgid ""
"2. Decode nodes — run on `$node_d0_ip`, `$node_d1_ip`, `$node_d2_ip`, "
"`$node_d3_ip` with `--dp-rank-start` `0/2/4/6`:"
msgstr ""
"2. 解码节点 — 在 `$node_d0_ip`、`$node_d1_ip`、`$node_d2_ip`、`$node_d3_ip` 上运行，使用 "
"`--dp-rank-start` `0/2/4/6`："

msgid ""
"For request forwarding on this 8-node A2 layout, use 4 prefiller hosts (1 "
"endpoint each) and 4 decoder hosts (2 endpoints each) in the Request "
"Forwarding command below."
msgstr ""
"对于此 8 节点 A2 布局的请求转发，请在下面的请求转发命令中使用 4 个预填充主机（每个 1 个端点）和 4 个解码器主机（每个 2 个端点）。"

msgid "**Notice:**"
msgstr "**注意：**"

msgid "Some configurations for optimization are shown below:"
msgstr "以下是一些用于优化的配置："

msgid ""
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1`: Enable FlashComm optimization to reduce communication and computation overhead on prefill node. With FlashComm enabled, layer_sharding list cannot include o_proj as an element.\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FUSED_MC2`: Enable following fused operators: dispatch_gmm_combine_decode and dispatch_ffn_combine operator."
msgstr ""
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1`：启用 FlashComm 优化，以减少预填充节点上的通信和计算开销。启用 FlashComm 后，layer_sharding 列表不能包含 o_proj 作为元素。\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FUSED_MC2`：启用以下融合算子：dispatch_gmm_combine_decode 和 dispatch_ffn_combine 算子。"

msgid ""
"Please refer to the following python file for further explanation and "
"restrictions of the environment variables above: "
"[envs.py](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/vllm_ascend/envs.py)"
msgstr ""
"有关上述环境变量的进一步说明和限制，请参考以下 Python 文件：[envs.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/vllm_ascend/envs.py)"

